   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">We parade again at <text:span text:style-name="T69">2</text:span> to visit the range had to Harry about in the wet birth for <text:span text:style-name="T69">3</text:span> hours and then 5 rounds for grouping test made an 8”. Ha<text:span text:style-name="T69">d</text:span> another look around To<text:span text:style-name="T69">wn </text:span>in evening</text:p>
