   <text:p text:style-name="P58"><text:span text:style-name="T13">7/4/15 </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T69">Wed</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P60">Paraded 8.10 four <text:span text:style-name="T69">No1</text:span> examining post. Had a rehearsal <text:span text:style-name="T69">at</text:span> the ceremony in the square first and at up to the square it’s 8:50 had to stand still while all the g<text:span text:style-name="T69">uards</text:span> were inspected which took till 9:25 and most exhausting. As the adjutant carries to each guard NCO in charge has to st<text:span text:style-name="T69">e</text:span>p forward and repeat his guard present then follow the adjutant spent to get told off for the bad was the men have dressed themselves found the port a good one <text:span text:style-name="T69">guards</text:span> room index stem estimate it S term in it very good indeed to the us had to use off a period table and played a lot also got a lot of letters written. Kept in wood was also the day and I came in for a good but</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P56"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">I/p2<text:span text:style-name="T102">3</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">of not because the God was not smart enough. Again in the early morning of the office of the day turned up at 530 Found the Ctr. He had not got his list of canceled passes on him</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Went to the dentist when God was dismissed he boarded out to the left and lower jaw.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Friday the <text:span text:style-name="T15">9th</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">A day of notes on the end sees parade at 645 we had a minute inspection and I was caught napping had not shared name taken that led to a chat with infants.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">All sorts of things are being devised to smartness up. The adjutant is making the first attempt that has been made I have been in the courts to do something properly and he is doing it properly new paragraph Saturday the 10th <text:span text:style-name="T15">Sat</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">We had in every parade and Saturday for NCS men and I had to march round the square of some 20 sergeants informs and salute them this as a practice for the March passed in the grand place.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Went to the dentist again and he made a thorough job of stopping a tooth in my is</text:p>
