   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Monday, 12 April</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">Day after God went out to dinner in evening with Hannaford to a place recommended by M <text:span text:style-name="T91">L</text:span>e<text:span text:style-name="T91">b</text:span>el <text:span text:style-name="T91">of Baillcut A thorourly </text:span>French place frequented by French people only and having a regular, <text:span text:style-name="T91">clientell quite </text:span>genteel people. Gave a very good idea of the reputed French custom of dining in nice places.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Wednesday 14</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">We <text:span text:style-name="T91">were</text:span> inspected by the general commanding GHQ troops <text:span text:style-name="T91">available </text:span>men paraded <text:span text:style-name="T91">in line facing o</text:span>ver side of barracks, general salute <text:span text:style-name="T91">&amp;</text:span> minute inspection, whole thing went very well also the inspection of our altars afterwards. We had made our room look particularly <text:span text:style-name="T91">smart</text:span> back<text:span text:style-name="T91">ing</text:span> <text:s/>stove putting map on the walls.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Thur 15 <text:span text:style-name="T91">O</text:span>n guard <text:span text:style-name="T91">no17</text:span> examining po<text:span text:style-name="T91">s</text:span>t with Pearson <text:span text:style-name="T91">Ba</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T91">ton</text:span>n and names of decoy. Pearson is the same man who was at college with Dori he is quite a nice fellows so was back in but Norm Eide told not much care for he had a very good guard it was a beautiful day we sat outside and watch the lock operations. On Friday morning miles of French transports passed</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">I/p2<text:span text:style-name="T102">5</text:span></text:p>
