   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Perhaps accounting for by the fact that the French are with drawing from the Belgian from Belgian to make a way for us.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Friday the 16th</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">In the afternoon I got a pass with them a Hills and we set off to explore the neighborhood beyond our post. The County is flat and and interesting by numerous canals. Cottages are built on the banks and the cottages only was getting about is by boat. Always bows are the same type pointed bow and stern in the sort of cross between a pond and a canoe they use a punitive paddle made of a piece of flat wood nailed onto a pole they gave they got along in by pushing against the bank this week found as a clever business</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">We we have failed upon on the cost years to lend us about we started off on good style doing a bit of canoe paddling with the paddle of found in this slow and very tiring so we tried, the reorganized effort but as I say found it difficult however we had the wind with us and soon found ourselves out at Clarion days. We had a book out the rulings there but found them to scant call</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">I/p2<text:span text:style-name="T102">6</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">to be interesting. When we started back we found the wind made things very difficult indeed. We pushed onto other estimate where we had a drink and also balls along of court to tow the boat. We also observed in nature pushing his foot native pushing his foot salon from the bank. In between the two methods got our boat nearly home I then took to paddling again and we turned up in a great start much to the admiration of inhabitants who had not seen this method of propulsion before they’ve thought us wonderful but when then we told them we had been to Claire Martz we had hidden the court.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">It was a most enjoyable day and most interesting I had heard of much distrust but never been in one before as an instance of us they made the canals we saw a person coming back from the fields with the two horses and a plow in his boat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">April Saturday</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P58">Had large of a third fugitive of six men to send out the Jesus HQ port of us but annoyed with the Sgt. Maj. That miserable fellow with one is</text:p>
