   <text:p text:style-name="P68"><text:span text:style-name="T105">D</text:span>id not pra<text:span text:style-name="T105">rade</text:span> t<text:span text:style-name="T105">i</text:span>ll 9. <text:span text:style-name="T105">P</text:span>ut onto a maxing</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P68"><text:tab/>I found I had very given my stripes <text:span text:style-name="T105">(</text:span>temp pending confirmation<text:span text:style-name="T105">)</text:span> on <text:span text:style-name="T105">F</text:span>ndy 6<text:span text:style-name="T105">th</text:span> with <text:span text:style-name="T107">Jukes Lewington, and Groom.</text:span> these <text:span text:style-name="T107">were</text:span> first four of <text:span text:style-name="T107">the</text:span> whole new bunch <text:span text:style-name="T107">&amp;</text:span> should next in se<text:span text:style-name="T107">niority</text:span> to both. <text:span text:style-name="T107">S</text:span>lo<text:span text:style-name="T107">an Vink Adams Steel Stewart</text:span> and Rees came after us</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P68"><text:span text:style-name="T107"><text:tab/>T</text:span>he time in England Pass<text:span text:style-name="T107">ed</text:span> only to<text:span text:style-name="T107">o </text:span>quickly <text:span text:style-name="T107">M</text:span>other and <text:span text:style-name="T107">F</text:span>ather were both very well and Marjorie as beautiful as ever in every way th<text:span text:style-name="T107">ough </text:span>we did not have much time together. It was such a pleasure to see the English County again like we did on their bus ride to Maidstone. I thought the number of young men about was was shockingly less both in London and elsewhere but there are still undoubtedly hundreds of thousands who could be drawn upon. I did not find as many rematch all erroneous ideas about about the war hit everyone was astonished when I told them of the unfriendly attitude of the Flemish peasants. Nothing at home seemed in any way strange after our life out here but I found that I had rehab appetite at all</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">I/p<text:span text:style-name="T102">33</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P68">I took <text:span text:style-name="T15">on the</text:span> markers job.</text:p>
