   <text:p text:style-name="P68"><text:tab/>On guard at the G H Q tr<text:span text:style-name="T107">easury.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T107">T</text:span>here are two small tin boxes to guard which are left in the <text:span text:style-name="T107">guard </text:span>room and the <text:span text:style-name="T107">s</text:span>entry on the chair bench them. <text:span text:style-name="T107">W</text:span>e of course have a day in the same room. <text:span text:style-name="T107">I</text:span>t is a coming guard it is an <text:span text:style-name="T107">impossible </text:span>to tell the Sentry from the rest</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P68"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T108"><text:tab/>When I came off I got up </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">pass</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">&amp; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108">went off to the canals with </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">Grouse</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">&amp;</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> PC </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">H</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108">ills we set about with the idea of getting down to the </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">h</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108">ill b</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">y </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T17">St</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17">.-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T17">Memelin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109"><text:s/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108">to see </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">the</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> fortification there. There was a </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">strong wind</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">blowing &amp;</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">we</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> found it was difficult to get along we had an omelette lunch at and a restaurant by the canal after great deal of trouble and much t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">owing</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> succeeded in reaching the </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">h</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108">ill of the fortifications made it quite worth while they have made a perfect for</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> of it. We sailed part of the way back and got a very cold so when we turned into the last stretch PC I took to the panels together we would getting along the splendid pa</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">ce</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T108"> when </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T109">suddenly</text:span></text:p>
