   <text:p text:style-name="P68">the punt pole, which was lying in the boat with me and just over the edge, c<text:span text:style-name="T15">a</text:span>u<text:span text:style-name="T107">ght</text:span> in the bank and catching my legs threw me out to the boat at least one <text:span text:style-name="T107">by </text:span>went <text:span text:style-name="T107">over and my</text:span> body. I hitched at P.C and <text:span text:style-name="T15">my</text:span> arm came in contact with a <text:span text:style-name="T107">b</text:span>o<text:span text:style-name="T107">tt</text:span>o<text:span text:style-name="T107">m</text:span> I went no further. I c<text:span text:style-name="T107">l</text:span>ambered out <text:span text:style-name="T107">&amp; ran on to </text:span>the estim<text:span text:style-name="T107">inet</text:span> where we hi<text:span text:style-name="T107">red</text:span> the boat. The woman le<text:span text:style-name="T107">n</text:span>t me some clean clo<text:span text:style-name="T107">ths</text:span> but made main round the fire. I had <text:span text:style-name="T107">my dinner </text:span>the<text:span text:style-name="T107">re</text:span> an<text:span text:style-name="T107">d H</text:span>ills and <text:span text:style-name="T107">G</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T107">ouse</text:span> brought me down some dry clo<text:span text:style-name="T107">thes.</text:span> I was a funny bunny altogether</text:p>
